snippet.title: Sick Samurai - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2497020/Sick_Samurai/

Sick Samurai is a blindingly fast and bloody action game based on instant-death combat. Immerse yourself in lofi hip hop and retro anime aesthetics as you slash and dash your way to becoming the greatest fighter on the island.
